flowchart TD
  A[Schedule or manual GitHub Actions] --> B[JQL: VM To Do / In Progress GHAS tools]
  B --> C[Per ticket: parse repo + alert #]
  C --> D{Fetch GHAS alert}
  D -->|403/404| E[Post fetch-error comment]
  D -->|fixed/withdrawn| F[Fast path: close comment, no LLM]
  D -->|OK| G[Evidence layers + truth table]
  G --> H{force_verdict?}
  H -->|yes| I[Deterministic FP - skip Judge]
  H -->|no| J[Judge + Prosecutor + Critic]
  J --> K[Consistency gate]
  K --> L{Post comment?}
  L --> M{Auto-transition?}
  M -->|confidence >= tier floor| N[Jira status change]
  M -->|else| O[Leave ticket open]
